106
00:06:36,820 --> 00:06:40,870
- You want me to take them?
- Will you?

107
00:06:40,870 --> 00:06:44,260
If you are going, please go with the sales department ace!

108
00:06:44,260 --> 00:06:48,090
- What?
- You must go with Hayama! It's a must!

109
00:06:48,090 --> 00:06:53,390
It sounded like a "must". If not, she might kill me.

110
