227
00:13:17,470 --> 00:13:21,440
I was the first who knew him, and the first to---

228
00:13:24,510 --> 00:13:27,910
Please excuse me. I need to go to the washroom.

229
00:13:27,910 --> 00:13:29,720
Akamine...

230
00:13:30,520 --> 00:13:35,250
I want to know how you really feel.

231
00:13:36,250 --> 00:13:37,960
It's just as I've expected.

232
00:13:39,010 --> 00:13:41,980
It must be the case.

233
00:13:48,160 --> 00:13:51,450
It looks like Yamamoto is running out of battery soon.

234
00:13:52,560 --> 00:13:57,020
He's not that good a drinker.

235
00:13:57,020 --> 00:13:59,800
- Then, let's end here today...
- No way!

236
00:13:59,800 --> 00:14:04,470
- Eh?
- You both can still drink, right?

237
00:14:04,470 --> 00:14:08,510
I'll take care of Yamamoto and bring him home.

238
00:14:08,510 --> 00:14:11,030
However...

239
00:14:12,430 --> 00:14:14,920
Let's just do as she said, Koga.

240
00:14:14,920 --> 00:14:16,240
Eh?

241
00:14:17,330 --> 00:14:21,280
Akamine, please take care of Yamamoto.

242
00:14:21,280 --> 00:14:22,980
No problem!

243
00:14:22,980 --> 00:14:24,570
Okay, Yamamoto. Let's go.

244
00:14:24,570 --> 00:14:27,430
What? Where are we going?

245
00:14:27,430 --> 00:14:29,840
Let's go back, together.

246
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:32,730
Hold your bag, or can you do it?

247
00:14:32,730 --> 00:14:35,020
Let me hold it for you.

248
00:14:39,110 --> 00:14:40,650
Are you fine with it?

249
00:14:40,650 --> 00:14:42,020
Yes?

250
00:14:42,020 --> 00:14:45,180
You look a little sad just now.

251
00:14:46,560 --> 00:14:49,150
There's no reason for me to be sad.

252
00:14:49,150 --> 00:14:51,330
Okay, what shall we drink next?

253
00:14:51,330 --> 00:14:55,380
Shall we see who gets drunk first?

254
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:04,440
I say, Hayami.

255
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:08,050
Don't take my blanket away.

256
00:15:18,070 --> 00:15:20,600
Oh my, it's cold here.

257
00:15:20,600 --> 00:15:23,090
Where is everybody?

258
00:15:25,880 --> 00:15:28,580
[Have a good rest. By Akamine.]

259
00:15:30,090 --> 00:15:32,010
